    <item>
      <title>Boaz Weinstein警告破产中的尖峰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/boaz-weinstein-warns-of-spike-in-bankruptcies-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易战争引发衰退的担忧，全球市场承受着压力，这加剧了自库维德大流行以来股票最糟糕的一周。彭博电视台的Sonali Basak与Saba Capital Management的创始人和Cio Boaz Weinstein谈到了严重衰退的可能性以及可能的情况。他们在大西洋城的彭博著作《看涨》（Bullish）的一集中讲话，重点是游戏，（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/boaz-weinstein-warns-of-spike-in-bankruptcies-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 10:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰米·戴蒙（Jamie Dimon）说，应迅速解决关税政策问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/jamie-dimon-says-tariff-policy-issues-should-be-resolved-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[JPMorgan Chase＆amp;公司首席执行官杰米·戴蒙（Jamie Dimon）敦促迅速解决唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税引起的不确定性，并警告不要对美国长期经济联盟的潜在“灾难性”分散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/jamie-dimon-says-tariff-policy-issues-should-be-resolved-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉（Tesla）分享跌幅，分析师Ives削减了价格目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/tesla-shares-plunge-analyst-ives-slashes-price-target-43</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司（Tesla Inc.）的股票在周一早些时候延长了亏损，而Wedbush证券分析师丹尼尔·艾夫斯（Daniel Ives）将其对股票的目标股价降低了40％以上。克雷格·特鲁德尔（Craig Trudell）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/tesla-shares-plunge-analyst-ives-slashes-price-target-43</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 10:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商在“风暴之眼”中使用Tech造成更大的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-brace-for-bigger-losses-with-tech-in-eye-of-the-storm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统坚持认为，他不会从上周释放的关税中退缩，市场专业人士正在为最暴露于税款的公司而局限于最糟糕的情况。他们期望的是严峻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-brace-for-bigger-losses-with-tech-in-eye-of-the-storm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 10:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票市场词汇表：导航市场崩溃的条款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/what-is-a-margin-call-what-is-vix-glossary-for-navigating-a-markets-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）抵制扭转其贸易关税和面临衰退风险的主要经济体的压力，很难驾驶全球市场的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/what-is-a-margin-call-what-is-vix-glossary-for-navigating-a-markets-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 09:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国暂时禁止短暂卖给平静的股票市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/thailand-temporarily-bans-short-selling-of-shares-to-calm-market-m96w6qkl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将暂时禁止短暂销售股票，并收集其他股票交易规则，以遏制波动性，因为美国全球广泛关税的后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/thailand-temporarily-bans-short-selling-of-shares-to-calm-market-m96w6qkl</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 09:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自由落体的市场，三天的抛售擦出9.5万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，金融市场上的屠杀恶化了，压力大的投资者放弃了希望唐纳德·特朗普总统会改变他的关税政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密特朗普的集会随着关税野蛮风险资产而蒸发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在11月初选举赢得胜利以来，加密货币几乎消除了他们的所有收益，因为美国总统的关税袭击的后果引发了他发誓要参加冠军的资产类别的沉重销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税“死亡图”使华尔街面临严酷的现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资者班级＆Mdash; 拥有几乎所有股票的前10％; 在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易攻势时代，很快就会遵守其新的，艰巨的地位。从企业高管将其股票期权计算到亿万富翁对冲基金大亨以及介于两者之间的每个人，现在只是附带损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股票将进一步投入关税动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-04-06/markets-react-to-us-tariffs-china-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在2025年4月2日在白宫玫瑰园举行的贸易公告活动中签署了一项行政命令，对进口商品征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-04-06/markets-react-to-us-tariffs-china-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 18:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
